room_title: Escape room "Rameses Revenge" by Escape It Houston in Houston
room_address: 11501 Sam Houston Ste. B, Humble, TX 77396
room_description: Join this archaeological adventure into the Egyptian pyramids! At an ancient dig site, you accidentally activate a trap and the door closes, trapping you inside. You have an hour to escape, or be ready to face the wrath of the mummies! Ramses is already planning his revenge...
